<i>to sic that</i>

269
00:18:04.284 --> 00:18:06.186
<i>knife-happy</i>
<i>little junkie on me.</i>

270
00:18:06.286 --> 00:18:08.056
<i>Watch yourself, laddie.</i>

271
00:18:08.155 --> 00:18:10.390
<i>Now, Jack,</i>
<i>behave yourself.</i>

272
00:18:10.892 --> 00:18:12.459
<i>Sit down.</i>

