forgotten about me.

332
00:24:51.625 --> 00:24:53.928
My parents said you did.

333
00:24:54.028 --> 00:24:57.264
<i>Oh, baby, things just got</i>
<i>a little crazy being back.</i>

334
00:25:00.101 --> 00:25:02.403
